ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of the Industry of EDWARD (TED) GORDON of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Jean Martel, effective December 11, 2013.
